FBIS4-22015 "jptot016__l94072" JPRS-TOT-94-016-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 13 April 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA RUSSIA Bomb on Moscow-Baku Train Kills Four Bomb on Moscow-Baku Train Kills Four LD1304084694 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 0800 GMT 13 Apr 94 LD1304084694 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Russian BFN [Text] There was an explosion last night at Dagestanskiye's Ogni train station near Derbent in one of the cars of passenger train no. 192 travelling from Moscow to Baku. INTERFAX was told by the Russian Ministry for Emergencies' press service that as a result of the explosion and the ensuing fire the car was completely burned out. According to preliminary data, four people were killed and one received injuries and burns.
